<subSubSection id="C368652E93538E0EF2AAFD8FFAAFFD90" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593538E0EF2AAFD8FFAAFFD90" blockId="10.[151,1437,541,964]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">
<materialsCitation id="3B1A3CF893538E0EF2AAFD8FFAABFD90" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798147301" collectorName="J. Serrano" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" specimenCount="2" typeStatus="lectotype">
The specimen here designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793538E0EF034FD8FFDA1FDFC" box="[521,624,541,567]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">lectotype</typeStatus>
is a female bearing the labels: “female symbol”, “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF6A6FD8FFA98FDFC" authority="Stev." authorityName="Stev." box="[1179,1353,541,567]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsutulus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF6A6FD8FFADAFDFC" box="[1179,1291,541,567]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">hirsutulus</emphasis>
Stév.
</taxonomicName>
in Rus. mer. Caucase”, “Steven.” and “ 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793538E0EF3CEFDD3FDB7FD90" box="[499,614,577,603]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">Lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF0B6FDD3FB56FD90" authority="Dejean, 1829" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1829" box="[651,1159,577,603]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsutulus" subGenus="Ophonus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF0B6FDD3FC3AFD90" box="[651,1003,577,603]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">Harpalus (Ophonus) hirsutulus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF1CFFDD3FB56FD90" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[1010,1159,577,603]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
desig. by 
<collectorName id="2687537393538E0EF6C7FDD0FAA1FD90" box="[1274,1392,577,604]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">J. Serrano</collectorName>
”
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C368652E93538E0EF2FAFDF7FE90FC08" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593538E0EF2FAFDF7FEFEFD0C" blockId="10.[151,1437,541,964]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF2FAFDF7FEB9FDB4" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[199,360,613,639]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean (1829)</bibRefCitation>
described this species based on 
<specimenCount id="9D74FD2C93538E0EF0EEFDF7FC53FDB4" box="[723,898,613,639]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" type="generic">four specimens</specimenCount>
: 
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF1B1FDF4FC7EFD68" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">Je possède quatre individus de cette espèce: le premier m’a été envoyé par M. Stéven, comme venant du Caucase...</emphasis>
. The first mentioned is hereby designed as the 
<typeStatus id="54C9880793538E0EF2FDFD3FFEFBFD0C" box="[192,298,685,711]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593538E0EF2FAFD43FB2CFC9C" blockId="10.[151,1437,541,964]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">
The species is currently named as 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF075FD43FB67FD20" authority="(Dejean, 1829)" baseAuthorityName="Dejean" baseAuthorityYear="1829" box="[584,1206,721,747]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Parophonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsutulus" subGenus="Ophonomimus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF075FD43FBD5FD20" box="[584,1028,721,747]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">Parophonus (Ophonomimus) hirsutulus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF62FFD43FB7CFD20" author="Dejean, P. F. M. A." box="[1042,1197,721,747]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" refId="ref10732" refString="Dejean, P. F. M. A. (1829) Species general des coleopteres de la collection de M. le Comte Dejean. Tome quatrieme. Mequignon- Marvis, Paris, vii + 520 pp." type="book" year="1829">Dejean, 1829</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF6FCFD43FF6CFCC4" author="Schauberger, E." pageId="10" pageNumber="494" pagination="69 - 72" refId="ref12124" refString="Schauberger, E. (1923) Zur Systematik der Carabiden-Gruppe Parophonus Ganglbauer. Entomologische Anzeiger, Wien, 3 (6), 69 - 72." type="journal article" year="1923">Schauberger (1923: 72)</bibRefCitation>
created the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF382FD67FDB3FCC4" box="[447,610,757,783]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Parophonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Ophonomimus">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF382FD67FDB3FCC4" box="[447,610,757,783]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">Ophonomimus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to include only this species according to the lack of pubescence in the paraglossa, mentum without median tooth, pronotum not emarginate posteriorly, etc. Then, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF681FC8BFA4DFCF8" author="Schauberger, E." box="[1212,1436,793,819]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" pagination="64 - 78" refId="ref12152" refString="Schauberger, E. (1933) Zur Kenntnis der palaarktischen Harpalinen (Zwolfter Beitrag). Wiener Entomologische Zeitung, 50 (1 - 11), 64 - 78." type="journal article" year="1933">Schauberger (1933)</bibRefCitation>
considered 
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF32AFCACFD83FC9C" authority="Reitter, 1899" authorityName="Reitter" authorityYear="1899" box="[279,594,829,855]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Parophonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="interstitialis">
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF32AFCACFE6BFC9C" box="[279,442,829,855]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">P. interstitialis</emphasis>
Reitter, 1899
</taxonomicName>
as a valid species and also included it within 
<emphasis id="B906EAB793538E0EF66FFCAFFB2CFC9C" box="[1106,1277,829,855]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">
<taxonomicName id="4C724D2693538E0EF66FFCAFFB28FC9C" box="[1106,1273,829,855]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Parophonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Ophonomimus">Ophonomimus</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593538E0EF2FAFCF0FB2FFCB0" blockId="10.[151,1437,541,964]" box="[199,1278,865,892]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">
Keys to identify the species are found in 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF0AFFCF3FCEBFCB0" author="Jeannel, R." box="[658,826,865,891]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" pagination="572 - 1173" refId="ref11231" refString="Jeannel, R. (1942) Coleopteres carabiques. Deuxieme partie. Faune de France 40. Librairie de la Faculte des Sciences, Paris, pp. 572 - 1173." type="book chapter" year="1942">Jeannel (1942)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF17BFCF3FC32FCB0" author="Sciaky, R." box="[838,995,865,891]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" pagination="37 - 65" refId="ref12215" refString="Sciaky, R. (1992) Revisione dei Selenophorina paleartici occidentali (Coleoptera Carabidae Harpalinae) (XXXVI contributo alla conoscenza dei Coleoptera Carabidae). Bollettino di Zoologia Agraria e di Bachicoltura, Serie II, 24, 37 - 65." type="journal article" year="1992">Sciaky (1992)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF624FCF0FB7AFCB0" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[1049,1195,865,892]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" pagination="344 - 386" refId="ref12516" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2004) Harpalina. In: Freude, H., Harde, K. W., Lohse, G. A. &amp; Klausnitzer, B. (Eds.), Die Kafer Mitteleuropas. Bd. 2 Adephaga 1: Carabidae (Laufkafer). Spektrum-Verlag, Heidelberg / Berlin, pp. 344 - 386." type="book chapter" year="2004">Wrase (2004</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF68BFCF3FB23FCB0" author="Wrase, D. W." box="[1206,1266,865,891]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494" refId="ref12634" refString="Wrase, D. W. (2011) Genus Tschitscherinellus. Arndt, E., Schnitter, P., Sfenthourakis, S. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (Eds.), Ground beetles (Carabidae) of Greece. Pensoft, Sofia, pp. 163." type="book" year="2011">2011</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCD36A593538E0EF2FAFC17FE90FC08" blockId="10.[151,1437,541,964]" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">
The species is distributed in Central Europe, the Mediterranean Basin, Central Asia and 
<collectingCountry id="F365763593538E0EF69FFC17FAF1FC54" box="[1186,1312,901,927]" name="Uzbekistan" pageId="10" pageNumber="494">Uzbekistan</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFE34B5493538E0EF713FC17FEE5FC08" author="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W." pageId="10" pageNumber="494" pagination="1810" refId="ref11718" refString="Kataev, B. M. &amp; Wrase, D. W. (2017 c) Subtribe Harpalina Bonelli, 1810. In: Lobl, I. &amp; Lobl, D. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. Vol. 1. Revised and Updated Edition. Brill, Leiden, pp. 515 - 562." type="book chapter" year="2017">Kataev &amp; Wrase, 2017c</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
